alue from arrow function.","ArrowFunctionExpression","expectedInside","'setIsLogin' is assigned a value but never used.","'error' is assigned a value but never used.","eqeqeq","Expected '===' and instead saw '=='.","unexpected","react-hooks/exhaustive-deps","React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'apiFunc'. Either include it or remove the dependency array. If 'apiFunc' changes too often, find the parent component that defines it and wrap that definition in useCallback.","ArrayExpression",["213"],"'Button' is defined but never used.","React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'clearErrors' and 'resetCategory'. Either include them or remove the dependency array.",["214"],"'saveClick' is assigned a value but never used.","no-global-assign","no-unsafe-negation",{"desc":"215","fix":"216"},{"desc":"217","fix":"218"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [apiFunc, depen]",{"range":"219","text":"220"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [clearErrors, initCategory, resetCategory]",{"range":"221","text":"222"},[575,582],"[apiFunc, depen]",[976,990],"[clearErrors, initCategory, resetCategory]"]